# Benchmark Baselines

Store historical benchmark results here for comparison purposes.

## Naming Convention
`v{VERSION}-baseline.json` - Full benchmark results for a specific release
`v{VERSION}-{DATE}-baseline.json` - Additional runs for the same version

## Example
```
v1.0.0-baseline.json
v1.1.0-baseline.json
v1.2.0-baseline.json
```

## Usage
After running benchmarks:
```bash
cp BenchmarkDotNet.Artifacts/results/*-report-full-compressed.json \
   test/WebDriverBiDi.Benchmarks/baselines/v1.0.0-baseline.json
```

These files can optionally be committed to git to provide historical reference,
or kept locally for your own comparison purposes.
